criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of chronic non-specific back pain for more than 12 consecutive weeks;

          -  Be sedentary

          -  Have not performed Pilates or Physical Therapy sessions for at least 6 months prior to
             the research.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of trauma or fractures in the trunk and lumbar spine;

          -  Diagnosis of osteoarthritis, degeneration of intervertebral discs, disc herniation and
             spondylolisthesis;

          -  Have undergone surgery on the spine;

          -  Presentation of neural root symptoms;

          -  Pregnancy
